[% global.title = 'Pass-through the primary video card to a KVM instance' %]

In short:

@vfio-pci.ids=1002:699f,1002:aae0,1022:1487 video=efifb:off@

@qemu-system-x86_64 -enable-kvm -m 16G -rtc base=localtime,clock=host -device vfio-pci,host=07:00.0 -drive if=pflash,format=raw,readonly,file=/usr/share/qemu/OVMF.fd -vnc :0 -drive file=/dev/sda,format=raw -drive file=fat:rw:/boot/efi -device vfio-pci,host=09:00.4 -device usb-host,vendorid=0x1c4f,productid=0x0002 -device usb-host,vendorid=0x093a,productid=0x2510 -usb -smp 8 -cpu host@

Mention @/sys/kernel/iommu_groups@ and having to pass-through whole groups.
